  <brief_title>Early Post-Marketing Study of ELIQUIS (Apixaban) in Mexico</brief_title>
  <official_title>Early Post-Marketing Study of Eliquis (Apixaban), in Treatment of Deep Vein Thrombosis (DVT) and Pulmonary Embolism (PE), and Prevention of Recurrent DVT and PE in Adults</official_title>
  <sponsors>
