  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of the study is to report adverse events of on-treatment AEs by the
      treating physicians during a specified 24-month study period in patients with venous
      thromboembolism at the sentinel site(s) for the National Center of Pharmacovigilance (CNFV)
      in Mexico.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
